							              <decoNote type="miniature">
								                <locus n="5r"/>The court poets of <name type="place">Ghaznī</name>: <persName key="http://lccn.loc.gov/no2006082934">'Asjadī</persName>, <persName key="http://lccn.loc.gov/n90711234">Farrukhī</persName> and <persName key="http://lccn.loc.gov/n82252330">'Unṣurrī</persName> approached by <persName key="http://lccn.loc.gov/n79094717">Firdausī</persName> in a garden (by <persName role="artist">Muzaffar 'Alī</persName>).</decoNote>
