								                <locus n="28r"/>
								                <persName>Garshāsp</persName> throwing <persName>Jaipāl</persName> off his elephant in battle.</decoNote>
							              <decoNote type="miniature">
								                <persName>Garshāsp</persName> fighting the sagsārs who are using tree branches as weapons (by <persName role="artist">Ṣādiḳī Beg</persName>).<locus n="45v"/>
							              </decoNote>
							              <decoNote type="miniature">
								                <locus n="74v"/>
								                <persName>Garshāsp</persName> seated before <persName>Ẓuḥḥāk</persName> while the dīv, <persName>Minharas</persName>, is held prisoner.</decoNote>
